reviewText: I specifically sought out this DVD due to the awesome nature of the 1st two movies in this series, however I have to say that this movie do not hold up the awesome reputation of the 1st two movies. It is too slow and hard to follow, plus for us BDSM lovers, it is nowhere close to the high expectations that the 1st two movies (especially the 1st movie) created. I have to sadly say that this movie is not worth you time or money. Sorry, but if the franchise were to return back to the format that made the first 2 movies successful, then it will be a worthwhile investment in the future. Plus the actress in the 1st two movies was awesome, a truly submissive.
